## 📌 Project Overview

This project is a **real-world SQL analytics case study** focused on IT industry sales performance. It demonstrates how raw transactional data can be transformed into **actionable business insights** using SQL.

💡 Built with a strong focus on:

* Business problem solving
* Real-world datasets
* Interview-level SQL concepts

---

## 📸 Project Highlights

✔️ 50+ SQL Queries (Basic → Advanced)
✔️ 7 Relational Tables (Fully Connected Schema)
✔️ Advanced JOINs, CTEs, Window Functions
✔️ 5 Real Business Case Studies
✔️ Revenue, Sales, Marketing & Customer Insights

---

