---

## 💡 Key Insights Generated

* 📈 **65% revenue from repeat customers** → Strong retention impact
* 🎯 **Referral channel = 3X better conversion than LinkedIn**
* ⚠️ **₹2.3 Cr revenue at risk** (unpaid orders)
* 📉 **Bottom 20% sales team → only 8% revenue**
* 📊 Identified exact **months of revenue drop & recovery**

---

## 🗂️ Dataset Structure (7 Tables)

* Customers
* Sales_Orders
* Order_Details
* Products
* Sales_Employees
* Payments
* Leads

---

## 🔍 SQL Concepts Covered

✔️ SELECT, WHERE, GROUP BY, HAVING
✔️ INNER JOIN, LEFT JOIN, Multi-table JOIN
✔️ Window Functions (RANK, ROW_NUMBER, NTILE)
✔️ Subqueries & Correlated Queries
✔️ CTEs (WITH clause)
✔️ Business KPI Calculations

